@using VanBanLuat.Librarys
@using ICSoft.ViewLibV3
@using VanBanLuat.Models
@model CategoryArticles
@if (Model.mCategory != null && Model.mCategory.CategoryId > 0 && Model.lArticle.Count > 0)
{
    int row = Model.lArticle.Count % 2 == 0 ? Model.lArticle.Count / 2 : Model.lArticle.Count / 2 + 1;  
    <section class="cat-box-section vien">
        <div class="title">
            <h2 class="td-phaply"><a href="@Model.mCategory.GetCategoryUrl()" title="@Model.mCategory.MetaTitle.TrimmedOrDefault(Model.mCategory.CategoryDesc.TrimmedOrDefault(string.Empty))">@Model.mCategory.MetaTitle.TrimmedOrDefault(Model.mCategory.CategoryDesc.TrimmedOrDefault(string.Empty))</a></h2>
        </div>
        <div class="cat-box-content">
            <div class="item-col2">
                @for (int i = 0; i < row; i++ )
                {
                    <div class="list-new">
                        <img class="thumb-bieumau" alt="@Model.lArticle[i].Title" src="@Url.Content("~/assets/images/icon-bieumau.png")" style="width:36px; height:40px;" />
                        <div class="pdbieumau">
                            <a class="post-title new" title="@Model.lArticle[i].Title" href="@Model.lArticle[i].GetArticleUrl()">@Model.lArticle[i].Title</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
            <div class="item-col2">
                @for (int i = row; i < Model.lArticle.Count; i++)
                {
                    <div class="list-new">
                        <img class="thumb-bieumau" alt="@Model.lArticle[i].Title" src="@Url.Content("~/assets/images/icon-bieumau.png")" style="width:36px; height:40px;" />
                        <div class="pdbieumau">
                            <a class="post-title new" title="@Model.lArticle[i].Title" href="@Model.lArticle[i].GetArticleUrl()">@Model.lArticle[i].Title</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                }
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
}